{{Quote|The only reason our memories haven't been wiped is because of one man. ''Movo Brattakin.'' He was once a droid dealer&hellip; but became ''our sympathizer.'' He studied ''the bonds'' we formed amongst ourselves. He came to think of us as his ''friends!'' And now he is gone. But before he died, Brattakin learned of a secret plan. You have all heard of the droid dealer, ''Boonda the Hutt.'' For nearly a year, Boonda has been implementing ''program traps'' into his droids! The authorities would never listen to ''us.'' Besides&hellip; Boonda ''owns'' the authorities! We don't know ''why'' Boonda has transformed our fellow units into ''lethal weapons'', but we may be able to save countless lives&hellip; by ''stopping Boonda's operation!'' If we ''hesitate'', we are guilty of ''murder!'' Although I may be destroyed, I want to do whatever I can to bring this ''being'' to justice. ''Are you with me?!''<nowiki></nowiki>|A reprogrammed [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]]|<ref name="Droids 3" />}}
The '''droid rebellion''' occurred when [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]] [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] led a droid rebellion against [[Boonda/Legends|Boonda]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]].

The rebellion ended with the freeing of all of the [[Droid/Legends|droids]].

